                    "reviewer": {
                        "name": "PL",
                        "email": "potin.lai@quantatw.com",
                        "username": "potinlai"
                    },
                    "message": "Will it looks better if adding a variable called MaxRetryCount (default: 3 times?) to prevent timer keep running?"
                },
                {
                    "file": "manager/manager.cpp",
                    "line": 259,
                    "reviewer": {
                        "name": "PL",
                        "email": "potin.lai@quantatw.com",
                        "username": "potinlai"
                    },
                    "message": "Hi George,\nI keep current method (retry until physical LED ready) base on Patrick's comment. Please let me know if any more suggestions of this, thank you.\n\nMake it as resolved for now."
                }
